{"tid":1960454,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【良心企業】曼聯唔用英國納稅人錢 孭起900員工薪金責任","createTime":"2020-04-06T07:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T08:23:25.000Z","uid":227801,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cc46f79b71c757025d39e6b1963a9754cadd0744","tid":1960454,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T07:28:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/wars/article/1_60801727?fromSource=Web&amp;utm_campaign=hkad_regular_entry&amp;utm_medium=internal&amp;utm_source=hkad_web&amp;utm_content=top_menu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fwars%2Farticle%2F1_60801727%3FfromSource%3DWeb%26utm_campaign%3Dhkad_regular_entry%26utm_medium%3Dinternal%26utm_source%3Dhkad_web%26utm_content%3Dtop_menu&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLQzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=2480be91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fwars%2Farticle%2F1_60801727%3FfromSource%3DWeb%26utm_campaign%3Dhkad_regular_entry%26utm_medium%3Dinternal%26utm_source%3Dhkad_web%26utm_content%3Dtop_menu&h=53606f86\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/wars/article/1_60801727?fromSource=Web&amp;utm_campaign=hkad_regular_entry&amp;utm_medium=internal&amp;utm_source=hkad_web&amp;utm_content=top_menu</a><br />\n2020.04.06<br />\n英國傳媒報道，曼聯將會繼同市球會曼城後，不會利用政府在武漢肺炎疫情的補助計劃，球會自己負起900名非球員員工的責任。<br />\n<br />\n早前紐卡素、熱刺及利物浦等球會先後用不同方案來逼員工放無薪假，利物浦就用政府資助來補貼員工，讓球會只負責員工2成的薪金，其餘8成就由英國政府負責，即是用英國納稅人錢出糧。<br />\n<br />\n據知曼聯已決定不用政府資助，自己負起薪金責任，向900名員工繼續支付全數薪金，球會將會在本周內向員工和外界公佈此安排。<br />\n<br />\n早在三月，曼聯已宣佈就算英超餘下賽季將會取消或閉門作賽，曼聯亦將會向所有球會的臨時工發薪，減少臨時工面臨收入不穩的危機，多達3,000名臨時工受惠。"},{"pid":"2372f8d4ca47691fd14cc99175b4891f25dd6562","tid":1960454,"uid":37085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T07:33:31.000Z","msg":"猁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad9fef7917ef88e1593482e09985e9ce6546b06","tid":1960454,"uid":272580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:23:25.000Z","msg":"一陣係狗竇度話獌本身都想, 只係遲左而家出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />扮好人"}]}